headline: Here's What to Expect From Hershey's Next Earnings Report
summary: Hershey is gearing up to release its second-quarter results later this month, and analysts are expecting a double-digit decrease in earnings.

headline: 3 Reasons to Sell HSY and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, Hershey has been a great trade, beating the S&P 500 by 5.5%. Its stock price has climbed to $168.32, representing a healthy 9.6% increase. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
